{html}<div><p>I spent about two hours doing numerous tests and could not get
it to work. I tried in the emulator and on my actual phone. Very
frustrating.</p>
<pre>
<code>Titanium.Gesture.addEventListener('orientationchange',function(e)
    {
       if (Titanium.Gesture.isLandscape(e.to))
       {
         document.getElementById("status").innerHTML = 'Stop Shaking me';   
       } 
       else if (Titanium.Gesture.isPortrait(e.to)) 
       {
         document.getElementById("status").innerHTML = 'Stop Shaking me';   
       }
    });</code>
</pre></div>{html}
